title: Spigot 1.14.4 服务器登录插件问题
author: 冯天语_Danny
txt_content:
[14:38:22] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] Enabling AuthMe v5.6.0-beta1-b2226
[14:38:23] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] SQLite Setup finished
[14:38:23] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] No supported permissions system found! Permissions are disabled!
[14:38:23] [Server thread/WARN]: [AuthMe] Aborting initialization of AuthMe: [InjectorReflectionException]: Could not invoke constructor of class 'class fr.xephi.authme.command.CommandHandler'
[14:38:23] [Server thread/WARN]: [AuthMe] THE SERVER IS GOING TO SHUT DOWN AS DEFINED IN THE CONFIGURATION!
[14:38:23] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] Waiting for 0 tasks to finish
[14:38:23] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] AuthMe 5.6.0-beta1-b2226 disabled!
好像有错误，加上AuthMe服务器就自动关闭保存
服务器插件有四个跨版本插件、AuthMe前置ProtocolLib和AuthMe的5.6.0版。中间我还试了加上luckperms，结果还是自动关闭保存
我用谷歌把日志汉化了一下，结果一目了然
